        {
            "id": 6011016,
            "title": "川馬鬧翻 特斯拉空頭單日獲利40億美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>在美國總統川普與特斯拉執行長馬斯克公開爭執導致特斯拉市值出現最大單日跌幅後，空頭交易員周四 (5 日) 從特斯拉 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSLA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSLA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSLA-US</a>) 股票的空頭部位中獲利 40 億美元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011016%2Fl%2Faf00d311d44f93fc916eb87691ddd777.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">特斯拉空頭單日獲利40億美元。（圖：REUTERS/TPG）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>分析公司 Ortex 的數據顯示，放空這家電動車製造商的收益史上排名第二。在該公司被納入<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">標普 500 指數</a>的審查時，交易員在 2020 年 9 月 8 日的拋售中獲利 54 億美元。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>該股周四收盤下跌 14.3%，市值蒸發約 1500 億美元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>空頭透過放空特斯拉獲利 75 億美元，這仍然是今年「七巨頭」股票中特斯拉的空頭投資人獲利最多的交易。根據 Ortex 的數據，蘋果以 73 億美元的收益位居第二。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
